title: Aaron Rodgers, Carmelo Anthony, Tom Brady, Jaguars, & the Blazing 5
itunes:title: Aaron Rodgers, Carmelo Anthony, Tom Brady, Jaguars, & the Blazing 5
description:
Colin discusses why Green Bay Packers QB Aaron Rodgers is like Golden State Warriors F Kevin Durant, why the Los Angeles Lakers don't need Carmelo Anthony, why New England Patriots QB Tom Brady is special, why the Jacksonville Jaguars could move and nobody would care, and the Blazing 5 picks for the weekend. Guests include DeAngelo Hall, Albert Breer, Eric Dickerson, Bill Burr, and Jason McIntyre.
